# {{{ Features:
# 4 virtual desktops
# vim-like window movement
# Tile windows to take up half the screen
# Easily switch between desktops and move windows between them
# Window styles to open on specific desktops
# Alt-tab behaviour and focus-follows-mouse
  # Alt-tab function is stolen from Packrat's fvwm config on the #! forums
# Network Manager integration via Stalonetray
# }}}
